# Real-Time Object Detection Android App

## 📌 Overview
This project is an Android application that performs real-time object detection using the device camera.

## 🚀 Features
- Live object detection using camera
- Displays bounding boxes and labels
- Fast and efficient processing

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Java (Android)
- TensorFlow Lite / OpenCV (check your project)
- Android Studio

## ▶️ How to Run
1. Open in Android Studio
2. Build the project
3. Run on emulator or real device

## 📷 Output
Real-time detection of objects with bounding boxes on screen
